- Compiled Obligation (O-TBP-UI-REACT-VITE-01-ui-source-package): Is there concrete implementation evidence for O-TBP-UI-REACT-VITE-01-ui-source-package Ă˘â‚¬â€ť Materialize React (Vite) SPA package metadata for local candidate runs (TBP: TBP-UI-REACT-VITE-01)?
- Compiled Obligation (O-TBP-UI-REACT-VITE-01-ui-source-config): Is there concrete implementation evidence for O-TBP-UI-REACT-VITE-01-ui-source-config Ă˘â‚¬â€ť Materialize React (Vite) SPA bundler configuration for local candidate runs (TBP: TBP-UI-REACT-VITE-01)?
