**Steps:**
- Materialize tenant_role_assignments boundary handlers on AP runtime surfaces.
- Apply mock auth context extraction and tenant scoping at boundary ingress.
- Preserve policy hooks for role assignment governance and enforcement.
- Keep boundary contracts aligned to declared resource operations only.
