          OBL-AP-POLICY-ENFORCEMENT Ă˘â‚¬â€ť Enforce CP-governed policy decisions on AP runtime surfaces.?
        - >-
          Compiled Obligation (OBL-TENANT-CONTEXT-PROPAGATION): Is there concrete implementation evidence for
          OBL-TENANT-CONTEXT-PROPAGATION Ă˘â‚¬â€ť Propagate tenant context through the adopted carrier and reject conflicting
          carriers.?
        - >-
          Compiled Obligation (OBL-AP-AUTH-MODE): Is there concrete implementation evidence for OBL-AP-AUTH-MODE Ă˘â‚¬â€ť
