        - >-
          Compiled Obligation (O-TBP-AUTH-MOCK-01-claim-contract): Is there concrete implementation evidence for
          O-TBP-AUTH-MOCK-01-claim-contract Ă˘â‚¬â€ť Materialize the mock auth claim-bearing contract helper used by policy and
