      - >-
        Compiled Obligation (O-TBP-UI-REACT-VITE-01-ui-source-package): Materialize React (Vite) SPA package metadata
        for local candidate runs (TBP: TBP-UI-REACT-VITE-01)
      - >-
        Compiled Obligation (O-TBP-UI-REACT-VITE-01-ui-source-config): Materialize React (Vite) SPA bundler
        configuration for local candidate runs (TBP: TBP-UI-REACT-VITE-01)
      - >-
        Compiled Obligation (O-TBP-UI-REACT-VITE-01-ui-source-entrypoint): Materialize React (Vite) SPA source
        entrypoint for local candidate runs (TBP: TBP-UI-REACT-VITE-01)
